{"tid":1961375,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"波音宣布：華盛頓州生產基地將無限期停工","createTime":"2020-04-06T18:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T18:06:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3685160ba08374f77764d285aa8251573fedf2","tid":1961375,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:14:24.000Z","msg":"波音宣布：華盛頓州生產基地將無限期停工<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3124315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3124315&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lexFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=26cca169\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3124315&h=939bfa63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3124315</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情在美國延燒，美國飛機製造商波音（Boeing）公司表示，在華盛頓州的生產活動將無限期停工，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，波音（Boeing）公司表示，綜合對疫情發展、政府衛生部門的建議等評估，將持續暫停其在華盛頓州的生產活動，直至另行通知。波音在華盛頓州有約7萬名員工，此決定將影響其中約3萬名生產工人。<br />\n<br />\n波音在上月25日宣布2週停工，員工在原訂的這2週停工期間，波音將員工的帶薪休假增加到10個工作日，但在接下來的停工期間，員工必須轉換使用帶薪休假。此外，波音將在停工期間繼續為所有員工提供醫療福利。<br />\n<br />\n波音週日表示，全球16萬名員工中約有135名員工，檢測呈陽性。"},{"pid":"531a9c775a49c3893e00f66c9adc7c00c9ed5cee","tid":1961375,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"R AP"},{"pid":"866cb63da1cb31ecd235a4100a36d026dcb2477e","tid":1961375,"uid":196652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220f2a2ec70ea3fd0e0131ebe8e5609423b69ab4","tid":1961375,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"支那賠錢"}]}